text: Cow finger, cow finger, what sound do you make? Moo moo moo, moo moo moo, I moo in the field. Shee finger, shee finger, what sound do you make? Ba ba ba, ba ba ba, I ba all day. Dog finger, dog finger, what sound do you make? Or what sound do you make? Meow meow meow, meow meow meow, Under dog finger, what sound do you make? Away! One two three four five animals, Hey! What sound do you make? Pig finger, pig finger, what sound do you make? Oink oink oink oink oink oink, I oink in the mud. Horse finger, horse finger, what sound do you make? Nay nay nay, nay nay nay, I nay and run fast. Frog finger, frog finger, what sound do you make? Rip it, rip it, rip it, rip it, I rip it at night. Chicken finger, chicken finger, what sound do you make? Cluck cluck cluck, cluck cluck cluck, I cluck in the farm. Bird finger, bird finger, what sound do you make? Tweet tweet tweet, tweet tweet tweet, I tweet in the farm.
